Sue Hamilton (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sue_Hamilton_(actress) 0 Sue Williams (May 13, 1945 - September 2, 1969), also known as Sue Hamilton, is an American actress and Playboy magazine's Playmate of the Month for April 1965. Her centerfold was photographed by Ed DeLong and William V. Figge.
